events.name: Louisiana Tech Bulldogs at Florida Atlantic Owls

headlines.description: J'Mar Smith threw for 217 yards and a touchdown and Louisiana Tech beat Florida Atlantic 21-13 on Friday night to snap the Owls' 10-game home winning streak.
headlines.shortLinkText: Louisiana Tech ends FAU's 10-game home winning streak 21-13

events.name: Miami Hurricanes at Boston College Eagles

headlines.description: AJ Dillon carried it 32 times for 149 yards and a touchdown, Anthony Brown threw for a score and ran for another and Boston College beat Miami 27-14 on Friday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Dillon carries for 149 yards and a TD in BC's 27-14 win

events.name: Indiana Hoosiers at Minnesota Golden Gophers

headlines.description: Tanner Morgan passed for 302 yards and three touchdowns in his first career start, including the tiebreaking 67-yard scoring toss to Rashod Bateman with 1:34 remaining that gave Minnesota a 38-31 victory on a rainy Friday night after Indiana rallied...
headlines.shortLinkText: Morgan, Minnesota top Indiana 38-31 on late 67-yard TD pass

video.headline: Bateman scores game-winning 67-yard TD for Minnesota

events.name: Wyoming Cowboys at Colorado State Rams

headlines.description: Freshman Sean Chambers had his first career passing and rushing touchdowns and Wyoming eased past Colorado State 34-21 on Friday night in the Border War.
headlines.shortLinkText: Wyoming scores 21 unanswered in 3rd to win Border War
